Master Answer:
If your child is school-aged, you should have received a letter regarding vaccination status reporting. Please follow the instructions in the letter. If you didn't receive a letter or have questions,  contact your local health unit for instructions on how to submit your child's record. You can find the phone number for your health unit here.
